data.text:
The Clare County Sheriff’s Reserves presents Ronnie McDowell at Clare High School, Saturday, June 22nd at 7pm.

The Nashville native, known best for his tribute to Elvis Presley, “The King Is Gone” is bringing his country style to Clare, MI.

For tickets, call 1(800)-205-7174

Advanced tickets are $18

At Door tickets are $25

To learn more about Ronnie and listen to his music click here: https://ronniemcdowell.com/home
